usage: run.py [-h] [-name NAME] [-data DATASET] [-model MODEL]
              [-score_func SCORE_FUNC] [-opn OPN] [-batch BATCH_SIZE]
              [-gamma GAMMA] [-gpu GPU] [-epoch MAX_EPOCHS] [-l2 L2] [-lr LR]
              [-lbl_smooth LBL_SMOOTH] [-num_workers NUM_WORKERS] [-seed SEED]
              [-restore] [-bias] [-num_bases NUM_BASES] [-init_dim INIT_DIM]
              [-gcn_dim GCN_DIM] [-embed_dim EMBED_DIM] [-gcn_layer GCN_LAYER]
              [-gcn_drop DROPOUT] [-hid_drop HID_DROP] [-hid_drop2 HID_DROP2]
              [-feat_drop FEAT_DROP] [-k_w K_W] [-k_h K_H]
              [-num_filt NUM_FILT] [-ker_sz KER_SZ] [-logdir LOG_DIR]
              [-config CONFIG_DIR]

Parser For Arguments

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -name NAME            Set run name for saving/restoring models (default:
                        testrun)
  -data DATASET         Dataset to use, default: FB15k-237 (default:
                        FB15k-237)
  -model MODEL          Model Name (default: compgcn)
  -score_func SCORE_FUNC
                        Score Function for Link prediction (default: conve)
  -opn OPN              Composition Operation to be used in CompGCN (default:
                        corr)
  -batch BATCH_SIZE     Batch size (default: 128)
  -gamma GAMMA          Margin (default: 40.0)
  -gpu GPU              Set GPU Ids : Eg: For CPU = -1, For Single GPU = 0
                        (default: 0)
  -epoch MAX_EPOCHS     Number of epochs (default: 500)
  -l2 L2                L2 Regularization for Optimizer (default: 0.0)
  -lr LR                Starting Learning Rate (default: 0.001)
  -lbl_smooth LBL_SMOOTH
                        Label Smoothing (default: 0.1)
  -num_workers NUM_WORKERS
                        Number of processes to construct batches (default: 10)
  -seed SEED            Seed for randomization (default: 41504)
  -restore              Restore from the previously saved model (default:
                        False)
  -bias                 Whether to use bias in the model (default: False)
  -num_bases NUM_BASES  Number of basis relation vectors to use (default: -1)
  -init_dim INIT_DIM    Initial dimension size for entities and relations
                        (default: 100)
  -gcn_dim GCN_DIM      Number of hidden units in GCN (default: 200)
  -embed_dim EMBED_DIM  Embedding dimension to give as input to score function
                        (default: None)
  -gcn_layer GCN_LAYER  Number of GCN Layers to use (default: 1)
  -gcn_drop DROPOUT     Dropout to use in GCN Layer (default: 0.1)
  -hid_drop HID_DROP    Dropout after GCN (default: 0.3)
  -hid_drop2 HID_DROP2  ConvE: Hidden dropout (default: 0.3)
  -feat_drop FEAT_DROP  ConvE: Feature Dropout (default: 0.3)
  -k_w K_W              ConvE: k_w (default: 10)
  -k_h K_H              ConvE: k_h (default: 20)
  -num_filt NUM_FILT    ConvE: Number of filters in convolution (default: 200)
  -ker_sz KER_SZ        ConvE: Kernel size to use (default: 7)
  -logdir LOG_DIR       Log directory (default: ./log/)
  -config CONFIG_DIR    Config directory (default: ./config/)
